# Tauri dev-watcher ignores (gitignore syntax). Tauri watches the whole cargo
# workspace (this dir) to rebuild the Rust tray on source changes. The Next
# frontend (ui/) churns ui/.next on every compile/route request — without these
# ignores the watcher re-runs the tray binary on each cache write, thrashing the
# app (and orphaning a menu-bar icon per restart). The frontend hot-reloads via
# `next dev` independently; Tauri never needs to watch it.
#
# Globs (not bare folders) because tauri#8901: a folder pattern can fail to
# exclude files inside it.
ui/**
ui/.next/**
**/node_modules/**
target/**
